<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA11">
<l>oṉṟē niṉaintiruntē ṉoṉṟē tuṇintoḻintē</l>
<l>ṉoṉṟēye ṉuḷḷatti ṉuḷḷaṭaittē - ṉoṉṟēkāṇ</l>
<l>kaṅkaiyāṉ ṟiṅkaṭ katirmuṭiyāṉ poṅkoḷicē</l>
<l>raṅkaiyāṟ kāḷā matu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One thing I keep thinking of. One thing I have finished deciding.</l>
<l>One thing I have retained inside my mind. One thing, look,</l>
<l>is that which is [to be] the servant of of him with the hand joined</l> 
<l>by a churning light, him with a crown of moon rays, him with the Gaṅgā.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
